AI agents to use built-in tools, MCP, Plugins, APIs, and browser-captured websites.\",\"url\":\"https://octo-dock.com\",\"image\":\"https://octo-dock.com/icon-512.png\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"OctoDock\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\",\"description\":\"Free tier available\"},\"featureList\":[\"Task-shaped natural-language tool actions\",\"Built-in, MCP, Plugin, API, and website capability sources\",\"Agent, account, permission, and environment eligibility\",\"Attributable operation records and error recovery\"],\"sameAs\":[\"https://github.com/chaosmibu-blip/OctoDock\"]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is OctoDock?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"OctoDock is an API platform that lets any AI agent (Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor, or any MCP-compatible tool) operate all your apps through a single MCP URL. It provides unified authentication, smart parameter correction, error recovery, and cross-agent memory — so your AI remembers your preferences no matter which AI tool you use.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is MCP (Model Context Protocol)?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"MCP is an open protocol created by Anthropic that lets AI assistants connect to external tools and data sources. OctoDock is an MCP server — you add one URL to your AI tool, and it can instantly access all your connected apps like Notion, Gmail, Google Calendar, GitHub, and more.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How many apps does OctoDock support?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"OctoDock includes a built-in adapter catalog and can also accept self-hosted tools, MCP servers, Plugins, OpenAPI or API documents, browser captures, and website-derived capabilities. Availability is filtered for each agent and execution environment.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is OctoDock free?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, OctoDock offers a free tier with 1,000 MCP tool calls per month. This is enough for most personal use. A Pro plan is available for heavy users who need unlimited calls.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Does OctoDock work with ChatGPT?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. OctoDock works with any MCP-compatible AI tool including Claude, ChatGPT, Cursor, Windsurf, and more. Your app connections, memory, and preferences carry over across all AI tools.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How do I set up OctoDock?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Sign up at octo-dock.com, connect or import the tools you need, authorize an agent, and add the OctoDock MCP connection to that agent. OctoDock only presents capabilities that the connected agent can actually execute.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is my data safe with OctoDock?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"OctoDock stores the connection metadata, encrypted credentials, delegated policy, capability source records, and redacted operation evidence needed to execute and audit authorized actions. It does not expose credentials or one user's tool data to unrelated users or agents.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What is cross-agent memory?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Cross-agent memory means OctoDock remembers your preferences and usage patterns across different AI tools. If you tell Claude your default Notion database, ChatGPT will know it too. Your memory lives in OctoDock, not in any single AI — so switching AI tools doesn't mean starting over.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How is OctoDock different from connecting apps directly via MCP?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Connecting tools directly means managing separate schemas, credentials, errors, and environment constraints. OctoDock translates them into task-shaped natural-language actions, filters unusable capabilities, applies delegated policy, and records what each agent did.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I use OctoDock for my team or business?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. OctoDock supports organizations — create a team, invite members, and share app connections and custom adapters. Each member gets their own MCP URL with team-level shared resources. Enterprise features include custom adapters, private API integrations, and usage analytics.\"}}]}</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"__variable_246ccd __variable_c29908 antialiased\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$?--><template id=\"B:0\"></template><!--/$--></div><div class=\"min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4\" style=\"background:var(--od-bg)\"><div class=\"max-w-sm w-full text-center space-y-4\"><h1 class=\"text-6xl font-bold\" style=\"color:var(--od-line)\">404</h1><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold\" style=\"color:var(--od-ink)\">Page Not Found</h2><p class=\"text-sm\" style=\"color:var(--od-ink-soft)\">找不到此頁面，可能已移除或網址有誤。</p><a class=\"inline-block px-4 py-2.5 text-sm text-white rounded-lg transition-colors font-medium\" style=\"background:var(--od-primary)\" href=\"/\">回首頁</a></div></div><!--$?--><template id=\"B:1\"></template><!--/$--><script>requestAnimationFrame(function(){$RT=performance.now()});</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-053ebe00af8b778e.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><div hidden id=\"S:1\"></div><script>$RB=[];$RV=function(a){$RT=performance.now();for(var b=0;b<a.length;b+=2){var c=a[b],e=a[b+1];null!==e.parentNode&&e.parentNode.removeChild(e);var f=c.parentNode;if(f){var g=c.previousSibling,h=0;do{if(c&&8===c.nodeType){var d=c.data;if(\"/$\"===d||\"/&\"===d)if(0===h)break;else h--;else\"$\"!==d&&\"$?\"!==d&&\"$~\"!==d&&\"$!\"!==d&&\"&\"!==d||h++}d=c.nextSibling